Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷皇帝 阿圖爾·賈茲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其女兒將是他的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是肩負命運之人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命運?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡的存在 僅僅是個開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前方等待的是超乎人們想象的命運…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你 不過是件推動命運的工具罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背著棺材的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能乾脆哪裡掉著錢嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我拿你下鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這深山裡搞什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,襲…襲擊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰襲擊? 襲擊誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劫…劫路賊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉你又猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正處於無業中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒吃的東西果腹 所以跑來挖野菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窮人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領會 無業窮人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒說錯但令人火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你又在這種地方干什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那東西是棺材嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山 無人 好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 這個 假裝沒看到 沒見過 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那棺材裡裝了實物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成…你是個殺人犯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪人 不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅人! 柔弱的旅人!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地 戴爾索蘭特市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無比遙遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這山裡走多久了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般哪用走那麼久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明顯迷路了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,震驚的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上有錢不?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小偷! 窮人! 劫路賊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我是想你請我吃早飯我替你帶路啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以神不知鬼不覺地將你帶進城裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然看你這樣子 一輩子也別想走下山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨角馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…倒霉透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Moruzerun Moruzerun Emurun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zeburun Wamurun Tourun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 這玩意兒丟掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒絕 接觸不得 貴重品!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥? 什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 沒辦法 我收回前言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那棺材可千萬別放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}Moruzerun Moruzerun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想被它吃掉 就給我抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 肚子餓得使不出力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然 強硬 亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包紮 緊急
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是獨角馬 它不用多久還會襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 包扎 不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對甩不掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 無趣的一生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要死?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡 不畏懼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說真一點不怕 那是瞎話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我活著也沒什麼可幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這樣的世界裡 我就是個廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機杖?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你是魔法師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廢物 同樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 只會這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他 廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這個 能辦到 很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如 幹掉獨角馬?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要 時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法術式 起動中 移動 不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拖延時間就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要爭取到時間 你就能用魔法了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為鋼也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼故不怯 鋼故不惑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦逢敵 盡無一切躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為滅此兇器也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵血轉化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zeburun Wamurun Tourun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊 駑馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kokult elum Naikt inte Naint kum
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ee wam ee wam milta ru Kokult elum
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Naikt inte naint
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Milta ru
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利刃呀奔流吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Ripper
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告戰終
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為人也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生存! 兩人 生存!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 很強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還行啦 畢竟曾經是亂破師嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是廢物 發揮了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧 有你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 算是盡了份力…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新委託 帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字 你?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 托魯·亞裘拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡·賈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,訂正
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡·托勒龐特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是對不住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我能更好地使馭你 你也不至於葬身於此了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟打敗了棄獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什麼人物?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩兒應一直是獨自行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了協助者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驚愕的胃袋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,運動完肚子會特別餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且呀 能吃的時候不多吃點…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你錢夠吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就無問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而野菜 又在哪兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以為你終於肯幹活了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到沒去挖野菜 而是摘了個少女回來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已經有我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還和個如此水靈的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臉對臉 在這兒坐著吃早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺瀟灑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你整天整天也不去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在家裡無所事事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠我一個人維持家計啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不該吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這男的真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已忍無可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 等等 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺悟!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你誤會了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我誤會了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小女子愚鈍 還請開示一二吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 「不稱職的老哥」這個評價是跑不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把等候早餐的妹妹忘在腦後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光顧著自己大吃大喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還砸了我的店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且無論飯錢還是賠款
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都丟給剛認識的這女孩付賬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驚得我連氣都生不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:12:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你身上聞到濃濃的廢柴味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到了棄獸的襲擊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話 我真能相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 然後得這丫頭幫助 幹掉了它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棺材裡放著機杖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傷就是戰斗的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後請客吃飯 就是帶路的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委託 工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要 亂破師兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會想拒絕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 可我都多少年沒工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然要我幹活…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是去工作 還是被我製成標本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請選一條路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這兩條?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說 兄長你希望由我親手製成標本?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不得不工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎蒞臨寒舍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是羅伯特·阿巴爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是叫…亞伯力克·基烈特是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您年輕得令人驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本聽聞來的是克里曼機關的人 我還以為定是位老者呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到基烈特家 那可是大大的名門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何要從事這份工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下對自己現在日夜為其奔走的工作感到自豪和責任感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉我問了個失禮的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了請問 此次造訪所為何事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下很清楚我們初次見面此舉顯得十分唐突無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一事不得不相求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽聞您乃討伐賈茲皇帝的八英雄之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想請您將在賈茲帝國帝都攻防戰一役中得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「戰利品」交予在下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我將戰利品 返還?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問 為何需要它?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕在下由於事需保密 不能告知您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿巴爾特伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的心情我十分理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 此問題不僅關係到維馬克王國
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至攸關整個菲爾畢斯特大陸的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今要我返還?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作 不花時間 簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領主 阿巴爾特伯爵府邸 襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並奪取
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了 我 就能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你腦子沒事兒吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常 需要 無論如何都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要做的事情 我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要做的事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做 義務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使耗費一生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要努力完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若要襲擊 那還得做很多準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說伯爵出身武門世家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天實際見面 我感到有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的意思是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看起來實在不像一位精通武藝之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰後五年 武藝生疏了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那宅子 也透著一絲古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何處古怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛兵的數量少得出奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以領主府邸來說 警備顯得太鬆懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺令人在意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕也是因為知道阿巴爾特伯爵是八英雄之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才來到這個城市的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 得到了協助者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許會動襲擊伯爵府邸的念頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我去監視嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是要偷什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不想說 我們也沒必要追問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們做好自己工作就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「工作」…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從兄長你口中聽到 真是有種奇怪的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個 房子西面的情況怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和東面同樣的結構
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到竟要和領主動手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長你怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說誰怕了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 兄長自然是渾身是膽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便手無寸鐵一絲不掛赤身裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也定能勇敢無畏笑迎千軍萬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那從各種意義上來說 都只是個傻子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是兄長你本人 也絕不允許侮辱我敬愛的兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 傻子應該是你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「就好」?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想潛進去好像不是很難
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但據說宅子的主人是在那賈茲帝都攻防戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為先鋒衝進城堡的勇士之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那想必是個不折不扣的武斗派啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得借助她的魔法力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到這個 那丫頭 真的可以信任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是委託人啊 還談什麼信任…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我指的是她作為魔法師的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那可是貨真價實的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰呀起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Burner
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麵包 大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:17:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛兵少得有點在意 不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照商量好的行事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面放著機杖是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攜入 必然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為鋼也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼故不怯 鋼故不惑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦逢敵 盡無一切躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為滅此兇器也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵血轉化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 和托魯一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打開棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 再用力推
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待遇 不正當
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 接下來怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要偷什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本能明白 我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就是要你讓我們也明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上 就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Efun Heluste Ru NBelguil Fai Sev
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯現吧 探測者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Locator
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的東西 宅邸中央
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散發 青白光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們分兩頭行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我負責一樓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 你和她負責二樓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是克里曼機關的手下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來對白天的鎩羽而歸 很是不滿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正為難得的寶物無處使用 而感覺稍許無聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛賊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…魔法師?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可和你們上司那騎士小少爺不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要過來 這傢伙是個魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法師?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要露臉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該已經死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.81,0:23:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途 終要起程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 會認真工作? 一絲不安
